items.title: Marijuana may produce psychotic-like effects in high-risk individuals
items.summary: Marijuana may bring on temporary paranoia and other psychosis-related effects in individuals at high risk of developing a psychotic disorder, finds a preliminary study.

items.title: New gravity map suggests Mars has a porous crust
items.summary: Scientists have found evidence that Mars' crust is not as dense as previously thought, a clue that could help researchers better understand the Red Planet's interior structure and evolution.

items.title: 'The dark side' of quantum computers
items.summary: The era of fully fledged quantum computers threatens to destroy internet security as we know it. Researchers are in a race against time to prepare new cryptographic techniques before the arrival of quantum computers, as cryptographers now describe.
